'''你们运动'''（{{lang-pl|Twój Ruch}}），在2013年10月6日前名為'''帕利科特運動'''（{{lang-pl|Ruch Palikota}}）是由前[[公民綱領_(波蘭)|公民綱領黨]]議員[[亞努斯·帕利科特|亞努斯·帕利科特]]（Janusz Palikot）領導的[[波蘭|波蘭]]政黨<ref name="10percent">{{cite news |title=10 percent support for rebel MP’s party? |author= |url=http://www.thenews.pl/national/?id=140903 |publisher=[[波蘭廣播電台|波蘭廣播電台]] |newspaper=TheNews.pl |date=5 October 2010 |accessdate=20 December 2010 |archive-date=2018-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181221041446/http://www.thenews.pl/national/?id=140903 |dead-url=no }}</ref>,，成立於2010年10月。媒體描述該黨為[[自由意志主義|自由意志主義]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.economist.com/blogs/easternapproaches/2011/09/polish-politics?page=1|title=From goggle box to ballot box|date=Sep 27, 2011|publisher=[[經濟學人|經濟學人]]|language=en|accessdate=30 October 2011|archive-date=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925222412/http://www.economist.com/blogs/easternapproaches/2011/09/polish-politics?page=1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wbj.pl/article-56388-palikots-surprise.html|title=Palikot's surprise|date=10 October 2011|publisher=[[華沙商業週報|華沙商業週報]]|language=en|accessdate=30 October 2011|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131229080056/http://www.wbj.pl/article-56388-palikots-surprise.html|archivedate=2013年12月29日}}</ref>、[[自由主義|自由主義]]<ref name="liberal1">{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/10/10/us-poland-election-palikot-idUSTRE79957R20111010|title=Liberal maverick to push for secular Poland after win|last=Borowski|first=Chris|date=2011-10-10|publisher=[[路透社|路透社]]|language=en|accessdate=30 October 2011|archive-date=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925113902/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/10/10/us-poland-election-palikot-idUSTRE79957R20111010|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="liberal2">{{Cite web |url=http://www.thenews.pl/1/9/Artykul/56350,Palikot-moves-into-third-in-race-for-parliament |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-01-08 |archive-date=2018-11-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181118175809/http://www.thenews.pl/1/9/Artykul/56350,Palikot-moves-into-third-in-race-for-parliament |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[反教权主义|反教權主義]]<ref name="anticlerical1">{{cite web|url=http://www.demotix.com/news/499935/anti-clerical-protest-gdansk|title=Anti-Clerical protest in Gdansk|date=4 November 2010|publisher=.demotix.com|language=en|accessdate=30 October 2011|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101110000325/http://www.demotix.com/news/499935/anti-clerical-protest-gdansk|archivedate=2010年11月10日}}</ref>、[[民粹主義|民粹主義]]<ref>{{Citation |1= |first=Nicholas |last=Kulish |title=Provocateur’s Strong Showing Is a Sign of a Changing Poland |newspaper=[[紐約時報|紐約時報]] |date=10 Oct 2011 |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/10/11/world/europe/polands-palikot-movement-signals-a-changing-society.html |accessdate=13 Oct 2011 |archive-date=2019-09-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190914132439/https://www.nytimes.com/2011/10/11/world/europe/polands-palikot-movement-signals-a-changing-society.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Citation |title=A glance at main parties in Poland's elections |publisher=[[美聯社|美聯社]] |date=9 Oct 2011 |url=http://hosted2.ap.org/vabrm/nationalworld/Article_2011-10-09-EU-Poland-Election-Glance/id-7e0bbcd254e6443081581cca7b2b7cb2 |accessdate=13 Oct 2011 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304023031/http://hosted2.ap.org/vabrm/nationalworld/Article_2011-10-09-EU-Poland-Election-Glance/id-7e0bbcd254e6443081581cca7b2b7cb2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>和[[左派|左翼]]政黨。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/polish-pm-seeks-coalition-partner-poll-win-14702677 |title=AP: Polish PM Begins Building New Government After Win |accessdate=2012-01-08 |archive-date=2011-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111012194936/http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/polish-pm-seeks-coalition-partner-poll-win-14702677 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5jm6KZMuYf6qFuYIrNCpAuSs-tAGg?docId=974625a9750b4137b1819e543c62fe9d|title=AP Interview: New Polish party on the rise|last=Gera|first=Vanessa|date=Oct 7, 2011|publisher=[[美聯社|美聯社]]|language=en|accessdate=30 October 2011|archive-date=2011-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111008072235/http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5jm6KZMuYf6qFuYIrNCpAuSs-tAGg?docId=974625a9750b4137b1819e543c62fe9d|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==歷史==
2010年7月，當時為[[公民綱領_(波蘭)|公民綱領黨]]成員的帕利科特表示已故總統[[列赫·卡辛斯基|列赫·卡辛斯基]]要對發生在[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]][[斯摩棱斯克|斯摩棱斯克]]的[[2010年波蘭空軍圖-154墜機事件|2010年波蘭空軍圖-154墜機事件]]負責。在具爭議的言論後，帕利科特宣布將籌組自己的社會運動。<ref>{{cite web|last=Wybranowski|first=Wojciech|title=Wirtualny Ruch Poparcia Janusza Palikota|url=http://www.rp.pl/artykul/16,507885.html|publisher=rp.pl|accessdate=2012-01-08|archive-date=2015-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150610201756/http://www.rp.pl/artykul/16,507885.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 10月2日，他在[[華沙|華沙]]舉辦「現代波蘭」大會，共有數千人參與。帕利科特在會中宣布15點綱領。<ref>{{cite web|last=Gądek|first=Jacek|title=Kabaret eksperymentalny Janusza P. z biskupami pasibrzuchami w tle|url=http://wiadomosci.onet.pl/tylko-w-onecie/kabaret-eksperymentalny-janusza-p-z-biskupami-pasi,1,3709724,wiadomosc.html|publisher=onet.pl|accessdate=2012-01-08|archive-date=2010-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101005033021/http://wiadomosci.onet.pl/tylko-w-onecie/kabaret-eksperymentalny-janusza-p-z-biskupami-pasi,1,3709724,wiadomosc.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>10月6日，帕利科特退出[[公民綱領_(波蘭)|公民綱領黨]]。<ref>{{cite web|last=Palikot|first=Janusz|title=I Resign (Janusz Palikot's blog)|url=http://palikot.blog.onet.pl/Skladam-rezygnacje,2,ID415472696,n|access-date=2012-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120426012641/http://palikot.blog.onet.pl/Skladam-rezygnacje,2,ID415472696,n|archive-date=2012-04-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

2011年1月9日，帕利科特將自己的議員身份證交給聖誕慈善大交響樂團拍賣。<ref>{{cite web|title=Palikot przed kamerami oddaje legitymację poselską na aukcję WOŚP|url=http://wiadomosci.gazeta.pl/Wiadomosci/1,80271,8921425,Palikot_nie_jest_juz_poslem___legitymacje_oddal_na.html|publisher=gazeta.pl|accessdate=April 6, 2011|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110112172910/http://wiadomosci.gazeta.pl/Wiadomosci/1,80271,8921425,Palikot_nie_jest_juz_poslem___legitymacje_oddal_na.html|archivedate=2011年1月12日}}</ref>

2011年6月1日，帕利科特正式登記新政黨「帕利科特運動」。[[2011年波蘭議會選舉|2011年波蘭議會選舉]]，該黨得票率達10%，拿下40席。<ref name="pkw2011-results">{{cite web | url = http://wybory2011.pkw.gov.pl/wsw/en/000000.html | title = Elections 2011 - Election results | publisher = 國家選舉委員會 | accessdate = 2011-11-13 | language = en | archive-date = 2011-12-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111214075746/http://wybory2011.pkw.gov.pl/wsw/en/000000.html | dead-url = no }}</ref> 選後，[[民主左派聯盟|民主左派聯盟]]議員 Sławomir Kopyciński 加入帕利科特運動。<ref name="kopycinski">{{cite web | url = http://wiadomosci.dziennik.pl/polityka/artykuly/362577,posel-kopycinski-z-sld-przeszedl-do-ruchu-palikota.html | title = Poseł Kopyciński z SLD przeszedł do Ruchu Palikota | date = 2011-10-20 | accessdate = 2011-11-13 | publisher = [[每日波蘭－歐洲－世界報|每日波蘭－歐洲－世界報]] | language = pl | archive-date = 2011-11-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111122063254/http://wiadomosci.dziennik.pl/polityka/artykuly/362577,posel-kopycinski-z-sld-przeszedl-do-ruchu-palikota.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>

==政治立場==
帕利科特希望終止[[公立學校|公立學校]]的宗教教育、終止教會的國家補助、[[墮胎|墮胎]]合法化、分發免費[[保險套|保險套]]<ref>{{cite news |title=Polish maverick MP launches anti-clerical party |first=Rob |last=Strybel |url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/idUKTRE6920W320101003 |newspaper=[[路透社|路透社]] |date=3 October 2010 |accessdate=20 December 2010}}</ref>、允許[[同性婚姻|同性婚姻]]<ref name="10percent" />、選舉制度改為[[聯立制|聯立制]]、改革社會安全局、解散[[波蘭共和國上議院|上議院]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Modern Poland's postulates on their website|url=http://www.ruchpalikota.org.pl/sites/default/files/rp.file_.3429.231.pdf|date=January 15, 2011|accessdate=November 20, 2011|language=pl|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111027034656/http://www.ruchpalikota.org.pl/sites/default/files/rp.file_.3429.231.pdf|archivedate=2011年10月27日}}</ref>、[[大麻|大麻]]合法化<ref>{{cite web |url=http://wolnekonopie.pl/idealistka/relacje-z-akcji/771.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-08-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111130091501/http://www.wolnekonopie.pl/idealistka/relacje-z-akcji/771.html |archivedate=2011-11-30 }}</ref>和推行[[單一稅|單一稅]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wbj.pl/blog/From_the_editor/post-312-what-does-palikots-big-win-mean-for-poland.htm|title=What does Palikot's big win mean for Poland?|date=2011-10-10|publisher=[[華沙商業週報|華沙商業週報]]|language=en|accessdate=30 October 2011|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111027032341/http://www.wbj.pl/blog/From_the_editor/post-312-what-does-palikots-big-win-mean-for-poland.htm|archivedate=2011年10月27日}}</ref>

